headline: DaVita HealthCare (DVA) Outperforms Broader Market: What You Need to Know
summary: In the latest trading session, DaVita HealthCare (DVA) closed at $106.3, marking a +2.28% move from the previous day.

headline: DaVita Inc. Schedules 4th Quarter 2025 Investor Conference Call
summary: DaVita Inc. (NYSE: DVA), announced today that it will hold its quarterly conference call to discuss fourth quarter results on Monday, February 2, 2026 at 5:00 p.m. Eastern Time. The company plans to release its results after market close the same day.
